{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-401-to-480/problem-447-retractions-c","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"project-euler-problems-401-to-480","demoType":null,"title":"Vežba 447: Vrati C","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Za svaki ceo broj $n > 1$, porodica funkcija $f_{n, a, b}$ je definisana na sledeći način:</p>\n<p>$f_{n, a, b}(x) ≡ ax + b\\bmod n$ za $a, b, x$ celobrojne i $0 \\lt a \\lt n$, $0 \\le b \\lt n$, $0 \\le x \\lt n$.</p>\n<p>Definišemo $f_{n, a, b}$ kao ako je $f_{n, a, b}(f_{n, a, b}(x)) \\equiv f_{n, a, b}(x)\\bmod n$ za svako $0 \\le x &#x3C; n$.</p>\n<p>Neka $R(n)$ bude broj povratnih vrednosti za $n$.</p>\n<p>$F(N) = \\displaystyle\\sum_{n = 2}^N R(n)$.</p>\n<p>$F({10}^7) ≡ 638\\,042\\,271\\bmod 1\\,000\\,000\\,007$.</p>\n<p>Pronađi $F({10}^{14})$. Daj svoj odgovor modulo $1\\,000\\,000\\,007$.</p>\n</section>","id":"5900f52c1000cf542c51003e","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Euler","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"project-euler","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":302119,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-401-to-480/problem-447-retractions-c"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function retractionsC() {\n\n  return true;\n}\n\nretractionsC();","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>retractionsC()</code> treba vratiti <code>530553372</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(retractionsC(), 530553372);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/project-euler/#project-euler-problems-401-to-480","dashedName":"problem-447-retractions-c","certification":"project-euler","disableLoopProtectTests":true,"disableLoopProtect